        new Stand( '908881', 'wall', 'Wall Mounted Display Stand for Square and Rectangular Projects}This is our newest wall mounted stand. Since it is made of two pieces the width is adjustable. Minimum project height is 6 1/2&quot; so keep this in mind when ordering. Holes for wall mounting. This stand uses our invisible style hooks that allow the stand to remain hidden behind opaque and semi-opaque pieces.', '8e204002931a481ea534e64ca394d338','multi', ['secondaryImg'=>'908801-stand-wall-5.jpg'], null, null, '908801-stand-wall-3.jpg', null, '15.96', 1),
        new Stand( '908810, 908812, & 908814', 'wall', 'Wall Mounted Display Stand for Plates and Bowls}Holes for wall mounting. With some muscle, stand can be bent outward or inward to fine tune size for your project. Can be adjusted up to 1&quot; larger or smaller. All Sizes same price because its all in the labor not the materials. Not only for displaying glass but ceramic or any material. Of course if you have a transparent piece, you will see the support bar through the glass. Can handle a slumped dish up to 1&quot;.', ['ded5260181244afa9917563e57047dca', 'ef82303210ca46918e62eff847e747eb', 'd9b6d5ac754a4980a603cb11ed02bbfc'], 'twin', ['secondaryImg'=>['wall-stand-glass-fusing-adjustible-sm.jpg','wall-stand-glass-fusing-adjustible.jpg'], 'clickImg'=>'display-stand-wall-12lg.jpg', 'secondary'=>['display-stand-wall-3pic.jpg']], null, null, 'display-stand-wall-12sm.jpg', null, [['1', '22.00', '10&quot; Project Size'],['2', '19.80', '12&quot; Project Size'],['4','17.60', '14&quot; Project Size'],['8', '15.40',null]], [1,1,1]),
        new Stand( '908708, 908710, 908712 & 908714', 'wall', 'Deep Dish Wall Mounted Display Stand for Plates and Bowls}Holes for wall mounting. With some muscle, stand can be bent outward or inward to fine tune size for your project. Can be adjusted up to 2&quot; wider or 2&quot; narrower. Support bar is adjustable and wire hooks are adjustable by bending. All Sizes same price because its all in the labor not the materials. Not only for displaying glass but ceramic or any material. Of course if you have a transparent piece, you will see the support bar through the glass. Can handle a slumped dish up to 2&quot;.', ['f878a8fbfa44497189c1fcb4bcba205f', 'b0a8aa9e784f4d8d8e63f8d86b9926be', 'ad99a282bc8e4f90a80fa4d8fb8aad36', '348d647dc922472dadce0ffe141ce687'], 'twin', ['secondaryImg'=>['wall-stand-glass-fusing-adjustible-sm.jpg','wall-stand-glass-fusing-adjustible.jpg']], null, null, '908712-12med.jpg', null, [['1','26.00','8&quot; Project Size'], ['2', '23.40', '10&quot; Project Size'],['4', '20.80', '12&quot; Project Size'],['8', '18.20','14&quot; Project Size']], [1,1,1,1]),
